## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources, which may not cover all aspects of the issue comprehensively. Additionally, some sources may have outdated information, and the rapidly evolving nature of technology and energy solutions could mean that newer developments are not reflected in this report. Further research, including interviews with industry experts and analysis of recent data, would provide a more in-depth understanding of the challenges and potential solutions.